---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet"
	pubDate={new Date("August 08 2021")}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>Who I Am</h2>
	<p>
		I'm a software developer with a passion for building robust web
		applications and scalable solutions. My journey in development has led
		me to specialize in creating dynamic, user-focused experiences that
		solve real-world problems.
	</p>

	<h2>My Technical Expertise</h2>
	<p>
		Throughout my career, I've cultivated a diverse skill set that spans
		both frontend and backend development. I have extensive experience with <strong
			>Laravel</strong
		> and <strong>PHP</strong>, which form the backbone of many of my
		server-side applications. My proficiency in <strong>Docker</strong> allows
		me to create containerized environments that ensure consistency across development,
		testing, and production stages.
	</p>

	<p>
		On the frontend, I'm well-versed in the fundamentals: <strong
			>HTML</strong
		>, <strong>CSS</strong>, and <strong>JavaScript</strong>. These core
		technologies enable me to craft responsive, accessible, and performant
		user interfaces that deliver seamless experiences across all devices.
	</p>

	<h2>What Drives Me</h2>
	<p>
		I believe in writing clean, maintainable code and following best
		practices. Whether I'm architecting a complex backend system or
		fine-tuning the user interface, I approach each project with attention
		to detail and a commitment to quality.
	</p>

	<h2>Let's Build Something Together</h2>
	<p>
		I'm always excited to tackle new challenges and collaborate on
		innovative projects. If you're looking for a developer who combines
		technical expertise with a pragmatic approach to problem-solving, let's
		connect and bring your ideas to life.
	</p>
</Layout>
